[
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "50",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03541\" class=\"\">This is what</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st>:<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"0335 02088\">Where</st> is your <st data-num=\"0517\" class=\"\">mother\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"03748\" class=\"\">divorce</st> <st data-num=\"05612\" class=\"\">certificate</st><p class=\"poetry\">by <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">which</st> I <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">divorced</st> her?<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0176\" class=\"\">Or</st> <st data-num=\"04310 0834\">to which</st> of my <st data-num=\"05383\" class=\"\">creditors</st> did I <st data-num=\"04376\" class=\"\">sell</st> you?<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02005\" class=\"\">Look</st>, you were <st data-num=\"04376\" class=\"\">sold</st> because of your <st data-num=\"05771\" class=\"\">sins</st>;<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">because of your <st data-num=\"06588\" class=\"\">rebellious acts</st> I <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">divorced</st> your <st data-num=\"0517\" class=\"\">mother</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "50",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04069\" class=\"\">Why</st> does <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">no</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">one</st> challenge me when I <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">come</st>?<p class=\"poetry\">Why does <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">no</st> one <st data-num=\"06030\" class=\"\">respond</st> when I <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">call</st>?<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Is my <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">hand</st> too <st data-num=\"07114 07114\">weak</st><n id=\"2\" /> to <st data-num=\"06304\" class=\"\">deliver</st><n id=\"3\" /> you?<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">Do</st> I <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">lack</st> the <st data-num=\"03581\" class=\"\">power</st> to <st data-num=\"05337\" class=\"\">rescue</st> you?<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02005\" class=\"\">Look</st>, with a mere <st data-num=\"01606\" class=\"\">shout</st><n id=\"4\" /> I can <st data-num=\"02717\" class=\"\">dry up</st> the <st data-num=\"03220\" class=\"\">sea</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">I can <st data-num=\"07760\" class=\"\">turn</st> <st data-num=\"05104\" class=\"\">streams</st> into a <st data-num=\"04057\" class=\"\">desert</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">so the <st data-num=\"01710\" class=\"\">fish</st> <st data-num=\"0887\" class=\"\">rot away</st> and <st data-num=\"04191 06772\">die</st> <p class=\"poetry\">from <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">lack</st> of <st data-num=\"06772\" class=\"\">water</st>.<n id=\"5\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "50",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I can <st data-num=\"03847\" class=\"\">clothe</st> the <st data-num=\"08064\" class=\"\">sky</st> in <st data-num=\"06940\" class=\"\">darkness</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">I can <st data-num=\"07760 03682\">cover</st> it with <st data-num=\"08242\" class=\"\">sackcloth</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "50",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"0136\">Sovereign</st> <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\">Lord</st></span> has <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">given</st> me the <st data-num=\"03956\" class=\"\">capacity</st> to be his <st data-num=\"03928\" class=\"\">spokesman</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">so that I <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know</st> how to <st data-num=\"05790 01697\">help</st> the <st data-num=\"03287\" class=\"\">weary</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">He <st data-num=\"05782\" class=\"\">wakes</st> me <st data-num=\"05782\" class=\"\">up</st> <st data-num=\"01242\" class=\"\">every</st> <st data-num=\"01242\" class=\"\">morning</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">he <st data-num=\"05782 0241\">makes</st> me <st data-num=\"05782 0241\">alert</st> so I can <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">listen attentively</st> as <st data-num=\"03928\" class=\"\">disciples</st> do.<n id=\"3\" /></p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "50",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"0136\">Sovereign</st> <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> has <st data-num=\"06605 0241\">spoken</st> to me <st data-num=\"06605 0241\">clearly</st>;<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0595\" class=\"\">I</st> have <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"04784\" class=\"\">rebelled</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">I have <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"05472\" class=\"\">turned</st> <st data-num=\"0268\" class=\"\">back</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "50",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">offered</st> my <st data-num=\"01460\" class=\"\">back</st> to those who <st data-num=\"05221\" class=\"\">attacked</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">my <st data-num=\"03895\" class=\"\">jaws</st> to those who <st data-num=\"04803\" class=\"\">tore out</st> my <st data-num=\"04803\" class=\"\">beard</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">I did <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"05641\" class=\"\">hide</st> my <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">face</st><p class=\"poetry\">from <st data-num=\"03639\" class=\"\">insults</st> and <st data-num=\"07536\" class=\"\">spitting</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "50",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">But the <st data-num=\"0136\">Sovereign</st> <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"05826\" class=\"\">helps</st> me,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05921 03651\">so</st> I am <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"03637\" class=\"\">humiliated</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05921 03651\">For that reason</st> I am <st data-num=\"02496\" class=\"\">steadfastly</st> <st data-num=\"07760 06440\">resolved</st>;<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know</st> I will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> be <st data-num=\"0954\" class=\"\">put to shame</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "50",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The one who <st data-num=\"06663\" class=\"\">vindicates</st> me is <st data-num=\"07138\" class=\"\">close by</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">Who</st> dares to <st data-num=\"07378\" class=\"\">argue</st> <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">with</st> me? Let us <st data-num=\"05975\" class=\"\">confront</st> <st data-num=\"03162\" class=\"\">each other</st>!<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">Who</st> is my <st data-num=\"01167 04941\">accuser</st>?<n id=\"2\" /> Let him <st data-num=\"05066 0413\">challenge</st> me!<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "50",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02005\" class=\"\">Look</st>, the <st data-num=\"0136\">Sovereign</st> <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"05826\" class=\"\">helps</st> me.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04310 01931\">Who</st> dares to <st data-num=\"07561\" class=\"\">condemn</st> me?<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02005\" class=\"\">Look</st>, <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> of them will <st data-num=\"01086\" class=\"\">wear out</st> like <st data-num=\"0899\" class=\"\">clothes</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">a <st data-num=\"06211\" class=\"\">moth</st> will <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">eat away at</st> them.</p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "50",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">Who</st> among you <st data-num=\"03373\" class=\"\">fears</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>?<p class=\"poetry\">Who <st data-num=\"08085 06963\">obeys</st><n id=\"1\" /> his <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">servant</st>?<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">Whoever</st> <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">walks</st> in <st data-num=\"02825\" class=\"\">deep darkness</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">without</st> <st data-num=\"05051\" class=\"\">light</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">should <st data-num=\"0982\" class=\"\">trust</st> in the <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">name</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span><p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"08172\" class=\"\">rely</st> on his <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "50",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02005\" class=\"\">Look</st>, <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> of you who <st data-num=\"06919\" class=\"\">start</st> a <st data-num=\"0784\" class=\"\">fire</st><p class=\"poetry\">and who <st data-num=\"0247\" class=\"\">equip</st> yourselves with<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"02131\" class=\"\">flaming arrows</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">walk</st><n id=\"3\" /> in the <st data-num=\"0217\" class=\"\">light</st><n id=\"4\" /> of the <st data-num=\"0784\" class=\"\">fire</st> you started<p class=\"poetry\">and among the <st data-num=\"02131\" class=\"\">flaming arrows</st> you <st data-num=\"01197\" class=\"\">ignited</st>!<n id=\"5\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02063\" class=\"\">This</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">is</st> what you will receive from <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">me</st>:<n id=\"6\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">You will <st data-num=\"07901\" class=\"\">lie down</st> in a <st data-num=\"04620\" class=\"\">place of pain</st>.<n id=\"7\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "11"
  }
]